96,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:21:04.000Z","msg":"銷售東江水予香港的價格較貴，平均每立方米5.8元；售予深圳和東莞平均每立方米1.1元<br />\n<br />\n斷水啦屌你"},{"pid":"f5fd4493cf04458b282c6441918600df9e36f27c","tid":1717160,"uid":285924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:21:59.000Z","msg":"而家劇毒東江水已由原本香港氯水消毒，改用中國漂水消毒，而承建商就係鄭x華律政師師長老公，無經正常招標途徑，左手交右手，各位好自為之，買個濾水器啦 。"},{"pid":"5423d882a3fb30cbbfb45fe269230f328eb5bc84","tid":1717160,"uid":73856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:26:31.000Z","msg":"要不是香港照顧你"},{"pid":"6f0a26f88ecaa71981c519b55564b693dac18475","tid":1717160,"uid":322775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:06:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b3282f3bf0c259b35da9804aad45889dcf8967f1","tid":1717160,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T07:11:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2eb3cc2ce14d4448e6a8e363ca8adb7be76092b8","tid":1717160,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T07:13:56.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}